00:33:52.560 --> 00:33:53.600
What is this?

00:33:54.320 --> 00:33:56.760
Mom told me to drink it and add water

00:33:56.920 --> 00:33:57.680
Add noodles if it's wet

00:33:57.880 --> 00:33:58.680
I...

00:33:59.160 --> 00:34:00.120
What should I do?

00:34:00.760 --> 00:34:01.720
Massage the dough.

00:34:01.960 --> 00:34:03.200
Be patient.

00:34:03.400 --> 00:34:04.200
Silly girl.

00:34:04.720 --> 00:34:06.360
You need to use your strength evenly.

00:34:07.280 --> 00:34:09.800
The noodles will taste better when kneaded.

00:34:10.000 --> 00:34:10.880
It's chewy.

00:34:11.040 --> 00:34:12.679
You don't even have this patience

00:34:13.679 --> 00:34:15.120
Speaking of which, kneading dough

00:34:15.520 --> 00:34:16.960
is the same as being a human.

00:34:17.800 --> 00:34:18.600
Mother.

00:34:18.760 --> 00:34:20.960
The noodles are dead and the people are alive.

00:34:21.239 --> 00:34:22.679
How can it be the same?

00:34:22.920 --> 00:34:23.880
Of course.

00:34:24.600 --> 00:34:26.000
Think about our world.

00:34:26.480 --> 00:34:27.800
People who can survive

00:34:28.000 --> 00:34:29.520
are people who have been hit.

00:34:30.159 --> 00:34:32.520
We've been through happiness and hardships

00:34:32.719 --> 00:34:33.719
in life.

00:34:34.080 --> 00:34:35.760
Am I right? Yes.

00:34:35.960 --> 00:34:37.560
Silly girl, think about it.

00:34:37.560 --> 00:34:38.440
right?

00:34:39.679 --> 00:34:40.960
Mother, you said it.

00:34:41.159 --> 00:34:41.920
I don't understand.

00:34:42.159 --> 00:34:44.080
I can't do this anymore. Let's go.

00:34:44.639 --> 00:34:45.400
Stinky girl.

00:34:51.480 --> 00:34:52.199
Eagle.

00:34:52.440 --> 00:34:53.920
I'm teaching you how to knead dough today.

00:34:55.280 --> 00:34:57.520
We can't live without food.

00:34:58.520 --> 00:34:59.440
One more thing.

00:34:59.640 --> 00:35:01.040
I just want to tell you

00:35:01.400 --> 00:35:04.280
to treat men with the strength of kneading dough.

00:35:05.320 --> 00:35:06.360
Men

00:35:06.560 --> 00:35:07.680
is like kneading dough.

00:35:08.080 --> 00:35:11.880
Dry it and add water. Add noodles if it's wet.

00:35:12.840 --> 00:35:14.040
You need to know your place.

00:35:14.720 --> 00:35:15.600
Okay?

00:35:17.040 --> 00:35:19.760
Min Ja why are you saying this all of a sudden

00:35:27.600 --> 00:35:28.560
Since you're here

00:35:29.440 --> 00:35:30.320
Come in and sit.

00:35:44.440 --> 00:35:45.520
When did you become

00:35:45.560 --> 00:35:47.120
so cautious?

00:35:49.320 --> 00:35:50.760
There are indeed a few things

00:35:51.080 --> 00:35:52.280
to tell you.

00:35:54.000 --> 00:35:54.840
Go ahead.

00:35:56.400 --> 00:35:59.400
One is your box of gold.

00:35:59.880 --> 00:36:01.120
There are indeed a lot.

00:36:01.920 --> 00:36:03.800
But no matter how much gold

00:36:03.880 --> 00:36:06.600
we won't have enough gold.

00:36:07.360 --> 00:36:08.240
I know.

00:36:09.040 --> 00:36:10.200
Don't worry about that.

00:36:10.680 --> 00:36:11.480
Also,

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:13.920
And that Wu Zhen.

00:36:16.640 --> 00:36:18.160
It was my fault

00:36:18.160 --> 00:36:19.120
I came up with this idea.

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:21.120
I told you two days ago

00:36:21.480 --> 00:36:24.080
there are a lot of gossip among our men.

00:36:24.080 --> 00:36:25.760
But you brought him to Black Tiger Mountain

00:36:25.760 --> 00:36:26.960
to be the head.

00:36:26.960 --> 00:36:27.800
In this way,

00:36:28.520 --> 00:36:30.560
it's not just the brothers.

00:36:30.840 --> 00:36:34.080
Everyone has a lot of words.

00:36:35.400 --> 00:36:36.560
It's nothing.

00:36:37.600 --> 00:36:39.480
They'll know in a few days.

00:36:40.040 --> 00:36:43.840
Wu Zhen is the most suitable candidate for Black Tiger Mountain.

00:36:45.520 --> 00:36:47.880
I know you must have a solution.

00:36:48.400 --> 00:36:49.840
But in the current situation,

00:36:50.160 --> 00:36:51.920
we don't know when the war will start.

00:36:52.640 --> 00:36:54.680
If we are not united,

00:36:54.680 --> 00:36:57.160
we'll be 100,000 swordsmen.

00:36:57.360 --> 00:36:58.400
However,

00:36:59.360 --> 00:37:00.680
it won't be that much.

00:37:01.200 --> 00:37:04.360
You just calculate too much in your room.

00:37:05.120 --> 00:37:07.760
You only know how to calculate.

00:37:08.080 --> 00:37:08.840
Let me ask you.

00:37:08.840 --> 00:37:09.880
If you beat the Japanese,

00:37:10.400 --> 00:37:12.920
do you think the Republican Party will win

00:37:13.200 --> 00:37:15.360
or the Communist Party?

00:37:16.080 --> 00:37:17.480
Why are you suddenly asking this?

00:37:17.720 --> 00:37:18.960
Answer me first.

00:37:20.800 --> 00:37:24.480
It seems that the army is stronger.

00:37:25.720 --> 00:37:27.040
I don't think so.

00:37:27.720 --> 00:37:29.800
Although the army has good weapons,

00:37:30.200 --> 00:37:31.480
but they have evil intentions.

00:37:32.080 --> 00:37:33.040
To put it bluntly,

00:37:33.560 --> 00:37:34.680
not like Communist Party.

00:37:34.880 --> 00:37:37.800
are fighting for the people.

00:37:38.600 --> 00:37:40.320
Brother, I'm confused.

00:37:40.920 --> 00:37:43.280
Aren't we talking about the head of Black Tiger Mountain?

00:37:44.920 --> 00:37:47.320
Now the Japanese

00:37:47.320 --> 00:37:48.800
of our country.

00:37:48.800 --> 00:37:50.400
We're almost at our door.

00:37:50.600 --> 00:37:52.720
We're still fighting over the mountain.

00:37:52.920 --> 00:37:54.240
We call ourselves swordsmen.

00:37:55.000 --> 00:37:56.920
The invasion is irreconcilable.

00:37:58.000 --> 00:37:59.240
In my opinion,

00:37:59.480 --> 00:38:00.880
the most important thing now

00:38:01.240 --> 00:38:03.320
Get rid of these invaders.

00:38:03.480 --> 00:38:06.200
I can't do it with 100,000 swordsmen alone.

00:38:06.720 --> 00:38:07.600
So I think...

00:38:08.040 --> 00:38:09.360
So you want to

00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:13.040
lead the swordsmen to join the Communist Party?

00:38:16.000 --> 00:38:17.280
Give Wu Zhen a chance

00:38:18.200 --> 00:38:19.680
to fight a war.

00:38:20.640 --> 00:38:21.920
to show his authority.

00:38:22.600 --> 00:38:25.200
If you're convinced, follow him.

00:38:25.720 --> 00:38:28.840
Those who refuse will not dare to make trouble again.

00:38:38.760 --> 00:38:39.560
Boss.

00:38:40.520 --> 00:38:41.280
Master Xi.

00:38:41.560 --> 00:38:43.400
Brigade Commander Cui sent something

00:38:44.920 --> 00:38:46.320
I just came back from him.

00:38:46.760 --> 00:38:48.480
He didn't say he would give us anything.

00:38:48.640 --> 00:38:49.480
Take a look.

00:39:08.200 --> 00:39:09.040
Li Gang.

00:39:13.280 --> 00:39:15.560
This is obviously not from Brigade Commander Cui.

00:39:18.720 --> 00:39:19.560
When did it come?

00:39:20.280 --> 00:39:21.880
About three hours.

00:39:26.560 --> 00:39:27.600
Take him back to Black Tiger Mountain first.

00:39:27.840 --> 00:39:28.480
Yes.

00:40:41.240 --> 00:40:42.760
Master of Water Village, Master Wu Liu.

00:40:43.480 --> 00:40:45.080
I went to the county for something.

00:40:45.320 --> 00:40:46.160
I'm late.

00:40:46.640 --> 00:40:47.640
You went to the county?

00:40:48.040 --> 00:40:48.840
Yes.

00:40:49.440 --> 00:40:50.560
Go find Choi Moon-Kui.

00:40:52.560 --> 00:40:53.280
Yes.

00:40:53.440 --> 00:40:54.880
Then you must have seen Li Gang.

00:40:57.840 --> 00:40:58.840
Yes, I did.

00:40:59.120 --> 00:41:01.120
But it's a corpse.

00:41:02.280 --> 00:41:03.480
How did you know?

00:41:04.720 --> 00:41:05.720
Wu Zhen.

00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:07.920
I didn't expect you

00:41:07.920 --> 00:41:10.120
to betray me.

00:41:11.280 --> 00:41:12.200
Masters,

00:41:12.600 --> 00:41:14.240
There must be some misunderstanding.

00:41:14.240 --> 00:41:15.400
Misunderstanding?

00:41:16.600 --> 00:41:18.080
You colluded with Cui Wenkui

00:41:18.440 --> 00:41:20.320
to instigate Li Gang to sow discord

00:41:20.320 --> 00:41:21.720
and hurt Liang.

00:41:21.720 --> 00:41:24.320
Today, you killed Li Gang with Cui Wenkui.

00:41:24.680 --> 00:41:26.560
You just want to buy my brother’s.

00:41:26.840 --> 00:41:28.080
so that you can sit

00:41:28.080 --> 00:41:30.160
the leader of Black Tiger Mountain?

00:41:30.920 --> 00:41:32.720
Trying to trick us?

00:41:33.360 --> 00:41:35.760
I'll avenge Liang today.

00:41:36.440 --> 00:41:37.360
Masters,

00:41:37.680 --> 00:41:39.880
Who told you that?

00:41:40.280 --> 00:41:41.040
Cut the crap.

00:41:41.720 --> 00:41:42.960
Tie yourself up.

00:41:42.960 --> 00:41:44.120
Let’s go to Qinglong Fortress

00:41:44.120 --> 00:41:45.600
and explain it to Leader.

00:41:45.600 --> 00:41:46.960
Madam asked me here

00:41:46.960 --> 00:41:48.240
to do something more important.

00:41:48.720 --> 00:41:49.760
After I finish,

00:41:49.760 --> 00:41:51.920
I’ll go to Qinglong Camp with you.

00:41:54.480 --> 00:41:55.280
Are you scared?

00:41:55.480 --> 00:41:56.360
I'm not afraid.

00:41:56.560 --> 00:41:58.240
I really have something important to do.

00:41:58.840 --> 00:42:02.120
I'm going to offend you two.

00:42:02.480 --> 00:42:03.280
Guards!

00:42:07.000 --> 00:42:07.920
What do you want?

00:42:09.480 --> 00:42:10.880
Remove them.

00:42:11.080 --> 00:42:11.920
I'll look at them first.

00:42:12.080 --> 00:42:13.520
Remember, serve her well.

00:42:13.880 --> 00:42:14.800
Don't slack off.

00:42:16.880 --> 00:42:17.840
Sorry.

00:42:18.120 --> 00:42:19.080
Masters.

00:42:19.600 --> 00:42:20.400
Please.

00:42:22.640 --> 00:42:23.840
You've got guts.

